828
00:42:14,680 --> 00:42:17,240
Basically, an ideal catch for most women.

829
00:42:18,480 --> 00:42:20,560
Most women, maybe, but I'm guessing

830
00:42:20,640 --> 00:42:21,960
that doesn't include you.

831
00:42:22,560 --> 00:42:23,960
Ms. Fang told me

832
00:42:24,600 --> 00:42:25,880
you prefer younger men.

833
00:42:29,800 --> 00:42:31,800
I used to.

